.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Transport: trike, train, skateboard, car, bus
Game: mah-jongg, backgammon, go, scrabble, monopoly
City: marseilles, rome, venice, paris, miami
House: trikemaster, tower, wooden, ranch-style, art-deco
Pet: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. Game:mah-jongg == Transport:skateboard
2. Game:swedish == Pet:dog
3. Game:backgammon == City:paris
4. Transport:train is on the left of Transport:car
5. Transport:train == City:rome
6. House:wooden == Pet:bird
7. Transport:bus == House:tower
8. City:venice is in the middle
9. Game:scrabble is on the far left
10. House:art-deco is on the left or right of Pet:cat
11. Pet:horses is on the left or right of House:tower
12. House:trikemaster == City:marseilles
13. Game:go == House:ranch-style
14. Game:scrabble is on the left or right of Transport:trike
15. House:art-deco is on the left or right of City:miami

